OL,3,CAmbulance service receives more than
OL,4,C13,000 emergency calls during heatwave
OL,6,FA critical incident, declared by South
OL,7,FEast Coast Ambulance Service last
OL,8,Fweek, following a period of "extreme
OL,9,Fheat" has been stood down.
OL,11,FSECAmb says demand for its services
OL,12,Frose sharply during the heatwave.
OL,14,FIt declared a critical incident on
OL,15,FFriday 26 June.
OL,17,FThe number of 999 calls handled
OL,18,Fincreased by 28% compared to the
OL,19,Fprevious week, with more than 13,600
OL,20,Fcalls answered over Wednesday,
OL,21,FThursday and Friday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
