OL,3,CAmbulance service receives more than
OL,4,C13,000 emergency calls during heatwave
OL,6,FIn Kent and Sussex, staff answered
OL,7,Fmore than 9,200 calls to 111, which is
OL,8,Fan increase of more than 10% across
OL,9,Fthe corresponding three days the week
OL,10,Fbefore.
OL,12,FThe Trust has thanked its teams for
OL,13,Fworking "tirelessly" during one of the
OL,14,Fbusiest periods SECAmb says it's ever
OL,15,Fexperienced.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
