OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1782827279
OL,3,CAmbulance service receives more than
OL,4,C13,000 emergency calls during heatwave
OL,6,FJohn O'Sullivan, Strategic Commander,
OL,7,Fsaid: "I would like to express my
OL,8,Fsincere thanks to our staff,
OL,9,Fvolunteers and support teams who have
OL,10,Fshown extraordinary commitment and
OL,11,Fresilience throughout this challenging
OL,12,Fperiod. Their dedication ensured we
OL,13,Fcontinued to provide care to those who
OL,14,Fneeded us most.
OL,16,F"While we have now stood down from the
OL,17,Fcritical incident as temperatures
OL,18,Fbegin to ease, we remain busy. We
OL,19,Fwould ask the public to continue to
OL,20,Fuse our services wisely."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
