OL,3,CAmbulance service receives more than
OL,4,C13,000 emergency calls during heatwave
OL,6,FSECAmb is urging people to carefully
OL,7,Fconsider whether they need an
OL,8,Fambulance response and to use 111,
OL,9,Fpharmacist or GP for medical advice
OL,10,Finstead.
